To install MergeTool in your system you have to execute merger_bash_helper.sh bash script in your terminal.
usage: merger.py [-h] [--verbose] [-ours | -theirs | -union] project_path

Resolves conflicts in a file

positional arguments:
  project_path  folder with the top-level Makefile

optional arguments:
  -h, --help    show this help message and exit
  --verbose
  -ours
  -theirs
  -union